citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:00am on 13-JUL-
23. Upon arrival at site, the inspector called the licensee. Licensee stated she was in Illinois at a dog show and could not
return home within 1 hour. The inspector then left the site.
End Section
